{"type": "article", "id": 20622, "title": "插头和插座钥匙扣", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-13T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702104006QRsPI1jgXkxbGmNW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组“插头”钥匙扣，配套的还有一个“插座”。它们都是橡木做的，“插座”安装在墙上，相应的挂钥匙的方式就是将插头插进孔里，简单且令人意想不到。橡木的手工感一定让不少人喜欢，而插头和插座的造型也非常少见，很有个性。带两个插头的售价 60 美元，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/boris-stecker-key-holder-oak-2-plugs/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150510uFh1a3n4rdQJbXe8.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150511K0RAbWuTc7L61Jlq.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"623\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66276596\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150511HXDMBJhqYZ9gfclw.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150512aIk396GnhiLtPjV4.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"627\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}